            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/13/the-obama-administration-is-forcing-local-cops-to-stay-silent-on-surveillance/#respond" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on The Obama Administration is Forcing Local Cops to Stay Silent on Surveillance">Leave a comment</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/4th-amendment/" rel="tag">4th Amendment</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/aclu/" rel="tag">ACLU</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/edward-snowden/" rel="tag">Edward Snowden</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/most-transparent-ever/" rel="tag">Most Transparent Ever</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/nsa/" rel="tag">NSA</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/unconstitutional/" rel="tag">Unconstitutional</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/13/the-obama-administration-is-forcing-local-cops-to-stay-silent-on-surveillance/#comments">0</a> 
