        <article id="post-9783" class="post-9783 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-news-items tag-aclu tag-edward-snowden tag-eff tag-illegal-spying tag-nsa-christmas-video tag-spoof clearfix rtp-post-box">
            
            <header class="post-header ">
                
                                            <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/12/13/video-of-the-day-the-nsa-is-coming-to-town/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Video of the Day: &#8220;The NSA is Coming to Town&#8221;">Video of the Day: &#8220;The NSA is Coming to Town&#8221;</a></h2>
                <?php// rtp_hook_end_post_title(); ?>

                
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-top"><span class="author"><a class="fn" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/author/mkriegs/" title="Posts by Michael Krieger">Michael Krieger</a></span> <span class="rtp-meta-separator">|</span> Posted <time class="published" datetime="2013-12-13T11:19:49+00:00">Friday Dec 13, 2013</time> at 11:19 am         <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/12/13/video-of-the-day-the-nsa-is-coming-to-town/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Video of the Day: &#8220;The NSA is Coming to Town&#8221;"><span>2</span> Comments</a></span>
            </div><!-- .post-meta -->            </header><!-- .post-title -->

            <div class="post-content">
                                

                
                <p>Just in time for the holidays, this excellent video spoof of the NSA has emerged. At the end of the day, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/09/17/video-of-the-day-the-iphone-5nsa/">humor is always</a> one of the most effective tools of resistance. Remember the wise and timeless words of John Lennon:</p>
<p><em>When it gets down to having to use violence, then you are playing the system’s game. The establishment will irritate you – pull your beard, flick your face – to make you fight. Because once they’ve got you violent, then they know how to handle you. The only thing they don’t know how to handle is non-violence and humor.</em></p>
<p>Enjoy.</p>
