get="_blank" title="Click to email this to a friend"><span></span></a></li><li class="share-print"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-print sd-button share-icon no-text" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/07/18/congressman-did-you-think-this-program-could-be-indefinitely-kept-secret-from-the-american-people-government-attorney-well-we-tried/" target="_blank" title="Click to print"><span></span></a></li><li class="share-end"></li></ul></div></div></div>
